title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Belarus Points of Interest, Belarus, 2008
name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Belarus Points of Interest, Belarus, 2008
description: Points of Interest in Belarus apparently includes fuel stops and parking. This data set shows various points of interest (about 340). most of which are fuel and parking spots, although it also includes toilets, bus stations, pharmacies, and post offices among other things.
